data.description: Entertain family and friends in this country style home located directly across from the Oakwood Country Club.  The long circle drive graces the front of the home which sits on approximately 1.31 acres.  The backyard is laid out perfectly for sitting outside on those warm Summer evenings.  Sip on a hot beverage in the colder months in the glass enclosed sun porch. Crown molding has been added in the living room, all of the bedrooms are nicely sized with the master bedroom on the main level.  The laundry room is located just off the kitchen.  2 car garage with new garage doors added in 2022, newer HVAC, heat pump, & humidifier.
